==Useful Info==
'''Cerulean imps''' are fast [[tier-5 demon]]s who always carry an enchanted [[spear]]. They can be summoned by the [[Call Imp]] spell.

==Tips & Tricks==
*Cerulean imps have a [[reaching]] spear, so they can attack from two tiles away. They can also attack when behind you.

==History==
*Cerulean imps were added in [[0.30]].

[[Category:Demon]]
